    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great in the driveway! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s all ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
