    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant paired with a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. This example boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal, addressing critical failure points. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the Guards Red paint shows minor road patina consistent with its driver-grade status, the chassis remains rigid and the variable valve timing (VarioCam Plus) provides a seamless power delivery through the rev range. A true driver\u2019s car with exceptional turn-in precision and a linear torque curve.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring premium upholstery that remains firm and comfortable, alongside a fully functional infotainment suite and crisp climate control. Mechanically, this car is a standout; it has been serviced at regular intervals, ensuring the engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts with precision. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. Whether you're navigating daily commutes or embarking on a weekend getaway, this car offers a reliable, refined, and quiet driving experience. It is a turn-key vehicle, ready for its next chapter with a discerning owner who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional merit, this specimen balances robust performance with a well-preserved aesthetic. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, the vehicle stands as a testament to consistent care and mechanical integrity. It represents a sophisticated opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber automotive investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
