    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and the interior is nice and clean. It\u2019s got a little bit of love and character from its time on the road, but it\u2019s been well-maintained and is totally ready for its next big adventure. I've priced it to sell because I'd love a quick, easy handoff to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Suspension remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, and the individual throttle bodies provide exceptional throttle response. Finished in Titan Silver over a clean interior, this driver-spec machine has been maintained with an emphasis on drivetrain longevity and performance dynamics.",
